===Etymology===
From the Tswana ''[[tsêtsê]].''
===Noun===
'''tsetse''' (''plural'' '''tsetse''' or '''tsetses''')
# (''entomology, South African English'') Any [[fly]] of the [[genus]] Glossina, native to [[Africa]], that feeds on human and animal blood and transmits the parasitic [[trypanosome|trypanosomes]].

